      edu.jhu.cs.damsl.engine.storage.page.Page<HeaderType>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ContiguousPage, PAXPage, SlottedPage
public abstract class Page<HeaderType extends PageHeader>
extends DuplicatedChannelBuffer

The basic unit of information transfer to/from disk. Pages are the fundamental unit of data retrieved and stored on disk during a single operation. They contain a number of tuples from a given relation, the exact layout of these tuples in the page depends on the type of page.
